citeinfo.title: Region of Peel Ward Boundary - 2014-2018

descript.abstract: Contains ward boundaries within the Region of Peel (2014-2018). Municipal elections are levied at the Ward level; councillors are elected from each ward to form Municipal and Regional councils.
descript.purpose: To delineate the current municipal wards in the Region, each of which serves as a geopolitical boundary which may be used for analysis purposes and for municipal election/governance purposes.
